DEVELOPMENT NOTICE

This project is actively under development by Starbound, an organization 
dedicated to advancing autonomous flight control systems and UAV technology.

For support, contributions, or collaboration inquiries:
- Repository: https://github.com/Starbound-Team/PID-controller
- Organization: Starbound Team
- Project: Drone PID Controller - Production-Ready Flight Control System

This software is provided for research, educational, and development purposes.
While designed for production use, users should thoroughly test and validate
all systems before deployment in safety-critical applications.

HARDWARE SAFETY DISCLAIMER:
This flight control software is intended for use with unmanned aerial vehicles.
Users are responsible for:
- Compliance with local aviation regulations
- Proper hardware integration and testing
- Safe operation practices
- Risk assessment and mitigation

The developers and Starbound organization assume no liability for damages,
accidents, or injuries resulting from the use of this software.
